<ab facs="#facs_285_r1l10">nehſt <expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd <expan>erfüre<ex>n</ex></expan> vvir <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> den <expan>lewffe<ex>n</ex></expan> ıht </ab>
