<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von
                                <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> samnung und gewerbe
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, als <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>yeczund<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sein, <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        ewrs <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreibens</expan>
<expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan> wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> mit <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        fleizze. Und <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, ob ir iht
                                <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> erfürt, wo hin
                            <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> auf wen <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> czug
                        sein solt, daz ir <add>uns</add> das aber
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet. Auch als
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>gnedige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> des künigs <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> von
                                <expan>Ung<ex>er</ex>n</expan> etc. wissen wir noch nicht
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan>, <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> als wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> nehst <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, und <expan>erfüre<ex>n</ex></expan> wir
                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> den <expan>lewffe<ex>n</ex></expan> iht,
                        das <expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir ewr
                            <expan>fruntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> auch <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
                        bey unsselbs <expan>bot<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>ut s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
<div type="cedula">
<ab>Cedula. Auch haben wir dem boten den lon gerichtet.</ab>
</div>
